5:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook: Kevin Hui<br />\n<br />\n中文名:許家偉<br />\n<br />\n中學:香港中文大學校友會聯會陳震夏中學<br />\n<br />\n大專:HKCC</span></span><br />\n<br />\n事源就係女朋友係facebook無啦啦有個三唔識七既人inobx佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kx8wuNP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKx8wuNP.png&h=507fbd36&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n仲要問一唔一齊出去,真係唔知咩心態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係facebook PO下新聞扮同路人<br />\n<br />\n實際上就係想借呢件事黎食女<br />\n<br />\n絲打真係要小心<br />\n<br />\n狗公ig:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NWNMVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NWNMVs.jpg&h=58c06442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條撚樣仲要好似有女朋友?<br />\n做佢女朋友真係慘<br />\n<br />\n絲打們認住呢條撚樣,踢波既 小心佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gc2k6Wh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgc2k6Wh.png&h=893df396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾狗公咁撚鍾意消費呢場運動?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r30ZC4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr30ZC4p.png&h=bda94586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返去玩玩具啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">絲打們要小心,好撚多呢種垃圾狗公借機搵食<br />\n<br />\n特別係呢條死狗公 許家偉!!</span>"},{"pid":"6ec12237bd765bc8b62c8dc1cbe339c96e5fd9b9","tid":1727718,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d22ce596b10b1ff298dcee9f9f6b187154a31e","tid":1727718,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29oP1r4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29oP1r4.png&h=98ecaa97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3081eb54fa31da3c68178e27deb61657f6cb1018","tid":1727718,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":